Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.12,0:00:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When watching "Hayate the Combat Butler",
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make sure you keep the room bright \Nand sit well away from the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.52,0:00:15.99,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}One morning, the boy found \Nhimself in the Twilight Zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.59,0:00:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.59,0:00:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.67,0:00:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.76,0:00:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Panning vertically!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A close-up horizontal pan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.29,0:00:36.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-It's Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:39.68,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what's with her outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.54,0:00:44.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kid, you're digging it, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:51.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! She's getting on \Na bus with no hesitation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.16,0:00:56.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-This can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.60,0:00:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I'm getting on!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.77,0:00:58.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go return the utility pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.35,0:01:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, whoops!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.80,0:01:02.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or Tokyo Electric Power Company \Nis going to yell at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.61,0:01:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.70,0:01:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.38,0:01:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm getting on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.46,0:01:10.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't make it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.43,0:01:12.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You brought that on yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.21,0:01:15.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.38,0:01:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on here?! Tell me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't come over often, but when you do,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you ask the most nonsensical \Nquestions, you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.06,0:01:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I mean, a blazer!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.52,0:01:27.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer to that is simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.37,0:01:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't seen Isumi lately, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.54,0:01:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, I've been busy \Nwith finals and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.07,0:01:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What you saw was a hallucination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.63,0:01:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A hallu...cination?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.49,0:01:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's got to be a hallucination!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:44.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, everyone in town \Nlooks like Isumi to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that's true! \NThat was definitely Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.93,0:01:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably fallen for \Na guy at another school,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so she's sneaking in by \Nwearing their uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.32,0:01:57.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the heck goes to such lengths?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.56,0:02:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we like in a "Hana-Kimi" sort of world,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.09,0:02:02.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where girls disguise themselves as \Nguys to get into all-boys' schools
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.50,0:02:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just to see a good-looking guy she adores.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.84,0:02:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're putting on an awfully nuanced \Nperformance at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.58,0:02:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I had no idea the world \Nhad progressed that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.11,0:02:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.88,0:02:15.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Technical High School
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.35,0:02:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether there's a school gate there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.05,0:02:16.71,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No vandalizing!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or a wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.49,0:02:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or nurikabe wall monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.11,0:02:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Climbing over them all is \Nwhat it means to be a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.58,0:02:22.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:23.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.37,0:02:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...that Isumi is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.64,0:02:27.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(328,250)}Do Not Climb
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.79,0:02:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...trying to climb over?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.73,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Up we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.70,0:02:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me, we could not \Nhelp overhearing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.46,0:02:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No worries.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't say it's entirely impossible,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but don't cases like the one you \Noutlined tend to be exceptional?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.50,0:02:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see the need to be \Nso hard on a boy in distress.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.51,0:02:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to mess with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.44,0:02:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, Isumi in a blazer getting on a bus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.73,0:02:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's too bad it's not a \Nsailor suit and a machine gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.57,0:02:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's way old.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds interesting, so go \Ninvestigate it for me, Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.88,0:02:52.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.72,0:02:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss, just because it sounds interesting...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.55,0:02:57.32,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you know, ladies and gentlemen?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:02.16,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That a humongous mansion like \Nthis exists somewhere in Tokyo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.16,0:03:05.34,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Miss's name is Nagi Sanzenin. And...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.27,0:03:09.31,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Her butler's name is Hayate Ayasaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They are both a bit clueless
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.08,0:03:13.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and both have a bit of the \Nwrong idea about each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.56,0:03:18.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but they share the immensely strong, \Nloving bond between servant and mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.78,0:03:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi's found some guy she \Nlikes?! Say it isn't so!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:23.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, what is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.05,0:03:26.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Zettai nante shinjinai!\N I don't believe in absolutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:29.60,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukanou nante nai! \NNo such thing as impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:34.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mirai wa hiraku te no naka ni aru\N The future is in the open palm of my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.06,0:03:40.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Honne o misecha make datoka \NStuff like, showing your true feelings means defeat
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:45.20,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Dentaku hajiku jinsei datoka\N Or a life tapping away at a calculator
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.87,0:03:50.70,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kokoro o itsuwaru kurai nara\N Rather than be false to myself like that
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:56.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Shichiten-battou baka-shoujiki mo kuuzen-zetsugo! \NI'll struggle to be uniquely naïve and honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.13,0:04:01.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Komatta kao o mireba ki-ni-naru shi\N If I see a troubled look, I'll be concerned
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.17,0:04:06.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Jinsei isogu riyuu mo betsuni nai shi \NAnd it's not like I've got a reason to hurry through life
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.43,0:04:12.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Takara no chizu wa kimi ni azukeyou \NI'll entrust you with the treasure map
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.06,0:04:18.36,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Juuou-mujin yori-michi datte tsukiau yo! \NI'll even keep you company on your free-ranging detours
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:21.44,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rakkii-sugiru tenkai \NA development that's way too lucky
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kotae wa mayowanai \NI won't hesitate to give my answer
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.24,0:04:29.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kantan sa! Subete wa kimi no tame ni \NIt's easy! It's all for you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:32.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Fuuhyou wa ki-ni-shinai \NI won't worry about the rumors
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Rettou-kan ni doujinai!\N I won't let a sense of inferiority get to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:39.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kakedasu shunkan wa ima koko ni aru \NThe moment to start running is right here, right now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His Name Is Magic Ball Pitcher Wataru!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Video Rental\NV Tachibana
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duskin today, Duskin tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.01,0:05:05.52,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Junki Takegami\NGaou Rangerman
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, I found "Ryukendo" \Nmixed in on the Toei sentai shelf!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.29,0:05:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.68,0:05:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.02,0:05:17.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Goodman
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, that is the shelf \Nfor Toho's superhero SFX films.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:27.08,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Toho Superhero SFX
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.65,0:05:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,More Shochiku films other than "The \NX" and "Goke, Body Snatcher"...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.04,0:05:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Superhero SFX is a genre you know well. \NHow could you make a mistake like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:36.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when you're so blatantly depressed...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.45,0:05:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to the Young Sir?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.12,0:05:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As his maid, I cannot just let this go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.69,0:05:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hayate...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.32,0:05:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was afraid he might be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.74,0:05:56.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Miss was feeding his \Nfears quite a bit, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:05:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that was the reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just that he won't come \Nto me for advice, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.20,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's probably because
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.34,0:06:09.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's easier for him to talk \Nto Miss Nagi, who is his age,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or some other equally trivial reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.04,0:06:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, as I suspected, being older is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.35,0:06:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am past 20 already, so perhaps it \Nmeans I am past my expiration date.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.53,0:06:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That is not the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're still at a luscious age! I \Nmean, even if you were married...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.36,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right to be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.33,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it ain't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.92,0:06:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I recall...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.02,0:06:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, pan. Keep panning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.38,0:06:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That uniform is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.07,0:06:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,146)}Shio
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.04,0:06:51.90,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if what Nagi said was right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.39,0:06:54.39,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Darn it! Thinking about it \Nisn't going to get me anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.40,0:07:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did not imagine such \Na turn of events, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.94,0:07:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This outfit stands out, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.78,0:07:11.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You always stand out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.68,0:07:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But under normal circumstances, I \Nthink he would've noticed us long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.02,0:07:19.49,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Next stop, Shiomi Municipal \NHigh School Main Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.41,0:07:21.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiomi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.60,0:07:22.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I am burning to get off \Nat the next stoooooop!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.04,0:07:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been a long time since I've \Nfound myself coming to this school...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.04,0:07:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isumi's... here...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! You can't keep Isumi and \Nme apart with something like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.61,0:07:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.44,0:07:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi must have been wearing their uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does he have to go to \Nsuch lengths for Isumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.11,0:07:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if only I could do something \Nfor the Young Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:08:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, if you'd like, shall I tell you \Nhow to get inside the school grounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.48,0:08:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it normal for butlers to \Nknow things like that, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.44,0:08:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it! Why won't the gate open?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.86,0:08:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's come to this, \NI'll do a vertical suplex...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.42,0:08:14.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:17.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.80,0:08:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That {\i1}is{\i0} part of my business.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have heard what is going on from Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think I could just \Nleave you to your own devices?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, ma'am! Please do as you see fit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, get into the school grounds \Nthrough the tear in this fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.26,0:08:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no tear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.58,0:08:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.27,0:08:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This cannot be! According to \Nthe map Hayate drew for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there isn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.24,0:08:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness! It has been completely repaired!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.39,0:08:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Wataru, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.51,0:08:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind. Could you just let us in?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:08:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.82,0:09:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Makariku Maharita! There!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.52,0:09:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.53,0:09:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm always barely on time, \Nso don't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:07.61,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you bragging?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.61,0:09:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.52,0:09:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.52,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when a man \Njust has to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, you can act \Ncool like Captain Okita,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.73,0:09:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it is lame when you are \Ncaught on the chain link fence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.82,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.28,0:09:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At any rate, might we ask you \Nto show us around the school?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, I don't mind, but it's \Na really normal school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.54,0:09:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-What is th-th-that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.55,0:09:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.21,0:09:37.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're delinquents.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, we're a normal high school, \Nso we have people like that, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.68,0:09:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a good boy you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.53,0:09:47.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Puppies are so awesome! They're \Nso soothing for the soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.05,0:09:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What fortune is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(306,126)}Shio
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen a female gang leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.87,0:09:58.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, because we're a normal high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.27,0:10:01.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, you don't see those these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}That's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.34,0:10:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-That smelled nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.46,0:10:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the fragrance of lavender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.68,0:10:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, because we're a normal high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we sometimes get a girl leaping through time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.89,0:10:13.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the anime version.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the Tomoyo Harada version.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.39,0:10:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be able to handle the rest, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.44,0:10:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to hurry back to the co-op, \Nor they'll be sold out. Later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.35,0:10:25.08,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Having said that, the \Ngirl cheerfully ran off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My heart is pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.81,0:10:32.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spin, spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear, oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.94,0:10:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This does not seem... to be the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.27,0:10:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.48,0:10:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Isumi not here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.09,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.62,0:10:43.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This also does not seem... to be the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.52,0:11:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This also does not seem... Ptewy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:04.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naturally, this is not a fan service episode
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.91,0:11:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Swimming, swimming, swimming along...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.64,0:11:07.53,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}made specially for the Isumi fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.53,0:11:10.64,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Isumi is searching for something here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.65,0:11:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where in the world could Isumi be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.97,0:11:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.00,0:11:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you straining like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.39,0:11:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.00,0:11:28.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Isumi dressed like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.83,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Young Sir? Whoa, whoa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.92,0:11:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only that, but at the \Nend of her intent gaze is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.86,0:11:41.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(471,138)}Senpai
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that guy with the face \Nthat makes you want to touch it
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and "senpai" written on his back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I imagine you do not watch \NDVDs along those lines, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is a standard move in youth dramas.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.72,0:11:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Senpai, please wipe your \Nsweat with this" attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.69,0:11:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.69,0:12:02.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the move that's \Nconsidered an endangered species
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.88,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in anime and TV shows, \Nand even in girls' manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.89,0:12:07.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "Senpai, please wipe \Nyour sweat with this"!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.09,0:12:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}You fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.45,0:12:09.96,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For you young'uns out there,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.96,0:12:12.71,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}try asking your Showa \NEra mothers and fathers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.94,0:12:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but I am \Nstill just a bit past 20, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The white towel is an essential \Nitem for a girl in love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is a symbol that says,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I will be there for your sweat \Nand tears of youth, senpai."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:26.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:28.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHOCK!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:32.55,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe I didn't really know who Isumi was.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.55,0:12:34.91,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That Isumi wanted that blue \Nset square sort of season
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.91,0:12:36.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}that the sun could give or withhold...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.73,0:12:38.73,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That she was looking for \Nthat experience of youth...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:43.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, the ardent passion of \Nyouth isn't flowing in my veins.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flowing in me is the murky blood of an otaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.81,0:12:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will the Heavens forsake me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun... is blinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.75,0:12:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, the sun is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.74,0:12:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sun...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:13:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ruru-ruru-ru ru-ta-wa. What is it in reverse?\N({\u1}Ru{\u0}ru-ruru-ru ru-ta-wa. Hantai kara yomu {\u1}to{\u0}?)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.27,0:13:04.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonto-ton-ton, favorite part? Roasted jowl butt.\N({\u1}To{\u0}to-ton-ton, suki na bui wa? Tontoro rou{\u1}su{\u0}.)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel shy about seeing \Nmy old friends again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to be careful, so no one spots me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.53,0:13:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.85,0:13:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been 7 seconds and 3 frames!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Nishizawa... Looks like you found me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.77,0:13:25.57,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is Hayate here? Could it be \Nthat maybe he's come to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.57,0:13:28.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Since it's come to this, it \Nmight be faster just to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.98,0:13:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has anything strange happened today...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Want some bread? It's half-eaten, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.56,0:13:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:44.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, really! What am I saying \Nat a time like this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.18,0:13:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.21,0:13:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.56,0:13:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I saw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean, other than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.32,0:13:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not much else has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.81,0:13:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a normal high school here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.14,0:13:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so there aren't any celebrities \Nor IT industry CEOs here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:14:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me for interrupting your meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.10,0:14:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.03,0:14:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's like the Seven Mysteries of \NShiomi High School, I could tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.82,0:14:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the manager of a certain \Nclub suddenly passed away,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:16.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all kinds of strange things have \Nbeen happening after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because of that, no one \Nwants to stay after school,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.56,0:14:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the managers quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.60,0:14:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone says it's the \Ndead manager's curse now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.84,0:14:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like those are all horror \Nstories I've heard somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.51,0:14:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's just a rumor, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.25,0:14:36.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could it be...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.85,0:14:40.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...that Isumi was asked to banish \Na spirit in relation to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.06,0:14:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.53,0:14:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you around!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the heck? So Hayate \Nwasn't here to see me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.87,0:14:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This yakisoba sandwich is making me tear up!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.08,0:15:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.21,0:15:16.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true, I don't have impressive pecs...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.14,0:15:18.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And sweat and tears aren't for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.21,0:15:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So... this was the place...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.09,0:15:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one... Not anyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:48.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one will be allowed to \Nwipe my senpai's sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:50.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.62,0:15:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.69,0:15:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can use my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You can see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.40,0:15:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.40,0:16:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}A hit! There's a hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.94,0:16:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that aside, what did you \Nmean? Go ahead with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.62,0:16:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may use my body as a medium \Nto make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.94,0:16:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? C-Can I really?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.95,0:16:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm a loser!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.98,0:16:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Loser
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.64,0:16:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.45,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just too blindingly brilliant!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.96,0:16:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a chance in...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You hit me! I've never \Neven been hit by my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.25,0:16:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do not say that line!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.16,0:16:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because this is not a \Nparody! This is your life!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.25,0:16:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir, are you really fine with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:49.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even said it yourself earlier, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.95,0:16:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That there are times when a \Nman just has to get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.99,0:16:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are times when a man \Nhas to face things head-on,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.52,0:16:57.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how great an \Nobstacle stands in your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.77,0:17:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.89,0:17:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how am I supposed to \Nface that great obstacle?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.37,0:17:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may not look it, but I have more \Nlife experience than you, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.01,0:17:15.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, when it \Ncame to a man-to-man fight...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.65,0:17:19.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:19.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was always a baseball match, \Nputting heart and soul into one pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.47,0:17:24.02,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hitting and hitting, and \Npitching and pitching!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.02,0:17:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Truly, fair and square! \NNo regrets in your youth!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.15,0:17:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.17,0:17:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, the Young Sir may sprout wings...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:42.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And maybe leap out of a window...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And because I'm kind of sort of the \NBible that teaches him about freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.64,0:17:49.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's fine. This is how it should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:53.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even she doesn't really \Nknow what she's saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.05,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}so even if there were a song that \Nhad similar-sounding lyrics,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:58.46,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it would merely be a coincidence. \NAh, a thesis, a thesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.46,0:18:00.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki, where did Wataru go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.65,0:18:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Young Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.16,0:18:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...has gone to fight a man's battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.30,0:18:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.65,0:18:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.56,0:18:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! What do you want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.35,0:18:22.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A baseball match!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.08,0:18:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting heart and soul into \None pitch for her white towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.83,0:18:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I request that you engage me \Nin an earnest duel between men.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.30,0:18:32.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will get his sweat wiped \Nby the manager with her white towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.08,0:18:33.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you can't just do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. I accept!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.10,0:18:53.11,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Watch me, Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to put everything I've experienced \Nin my life thus far into this one pitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.11,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare he get all fired up on his own?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.16,0:19:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reach for me! My...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.45,0:19:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.75,0:19:36.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm completely burnt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.34,0:19:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Young Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.50,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki, I've been defeated... \Nand I have no regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.16,0:19:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.31,0:19:50.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked up a good sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.29,0:19:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.17,0:19:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you have no more \Nregrets holding you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:08.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.81,0:20:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That must have been tough for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.97,0:20:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A job well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.75,0:20:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will escort you back to your residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.61,0:20:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I appreciate it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:26.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isumi, I... I mean, I myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.15,0:20:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wataru, you helped me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.88,0:20:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting him \Nwork up a good sweat.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.92,0:20:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.72,0:20:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Isumi appreciated what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.02,0:20:43.93,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't quite understand,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.93,0:20:45.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but it seems to have gone well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So in the end, it looks like I \Nwas making a fuss over nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.66,0:20:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lame, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.23,0:21:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were a fine young man today, Young Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.96,0:21:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You were cooler than \NI have ever seen you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.90,0:21:11.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.24,0:21:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We left the shop unattended.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.35,0:21:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Young Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.23,0:21:21.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.25,0:21:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Isumi was just working \Npart-time as a manager?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, apparently so.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.84,0:21:30.01,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After all, I can't tell her \Nthat Isumi was working...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.01,0:21:31.86,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...to banish the spirit of a dead manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.86,0:21:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that reality is \Nstranger than fiction,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.82,0:21:37.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but nothing {\i1}that{\i0} strange ever happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.27,0:21:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,True.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This doesn't leave anything \Nfor Tamori to comment on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, I agree, Miss Nagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:48.22,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, no, what happened was \Nactually plenty strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.22,0:21:51.28,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Next time, it looks like a rival \Nwill be appearing for Hayate.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.50,0:22:06.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Aisaretai fureraretetai\NI want to be loved, to feel that touch
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:11.64,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Motomeru bakari no kimochi wa\NThe sense of continually seeking
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.64,0:22:15.47,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hibi o kumoraseteta\NUsed to darken my days
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.14,0:22:23.07,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Kimi ni deau sono hi made wa\NUntil the day I met you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.03,0:22:32.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Namae yonde sora ni hibiku-youni\NCall my name so it echoes to the skies
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.99,0:22:42.67,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mayoi-michi mo kitto futari nara\NEven lost, with the two of us, surely...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:48.30,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsunaida te to te hanasanai\NI won't let go of your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.76,0:22:51.14,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mamoritainda\NI want to protect you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.01,0:22:57.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Saa ikou bokura wa\NCome on, let's go, we'll...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.39,0:23:09.24,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Ima o mitsumete aruki-hajimeru\N...look at the present and start walking
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Student Council Girl Trio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.34,0:23:28.05,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Lettering by Masumi Asano
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.45,0:23:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The student council girl \Ntrio's Butler Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.05,0:23:29.46,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,Butler Report
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.95,0:23:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, it's Izumi Segawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.63,0:23:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Risa Asakaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.82,0:23:34.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Explosion! I'm Miki Hanabishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today will be the last of the \NStudent Council Girl Trio specials.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.78,0:23:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These 3 weeks have flown by.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how many times I listen to \Nthis song, I still think it's a masterpiece.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.04,0:23:40.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, a masterpiece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.96,0:23:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It could even be featured on \Nthat New Year's music show!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.15,0:23:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It might even be as good \Nas our national anthem!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.40,0:23:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it should be turned \Ninto the show's theme song!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.35,0:23:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, time for the fan service shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.82,0:23:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, if you paste the 3 fan service \Nshots together, you get one single picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.08,0:23:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.98,0:23:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means we have no choice but to \Nuse it to create original merchandise!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.70,0:23:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Adios, amigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.26,0:23:59.23,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,224)}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.80,0:23:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hayate, you don't have to work anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.27,0:24:19.25,OS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\pos(174,307)}The next episode of \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.79,0:24:01.89,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that to say that you're firing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.89,0:24:03.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.27,0:24:04.95,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,It means you can take a break \Nfrom your butler duties
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.95,0:24:07.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,and focus on your studies \Nuntil exams are over.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:10.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I made arrangements just \Nfor such an occasion!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:12.40,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,For a new, temporary butler!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.40,0:24:14.72,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A pleasure to meet you. \NI am Mecha Butler No. 13.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:17.87,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, "Sure, Amuro May Have \NHad a Place to Return to, But..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.87,0:24:19.88,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,I am superior to him, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.29,0:24:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure, Amuro May Have \NHad a Place to Return to, But..."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.88,0:24:24.25,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Change! Switch on, one, two, three, with \N"Hayate the Combat Butler" next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.25,0:24:26.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
